**Speaker notes:**
This is the workflow you'll see every week. Notice how it touches all four IT CX sub-functions in sequence. Demand Mgmt owns intake and prioritization, Solution Design owns architecture, Delivery owns execution and UAT coordination, Service Mgmt owns go-live and closure. We'll trace a real ticket through this process during your shadowing week.

